The cast of Men Who Do Housework Photo: ICA new reality show Men Who Do Housework is set to hit Chinese streaming site iQiyi early this month, the site announced on Tuesday. As China's first show focusing on taking care of the home, Men Who Do Housework features three celebrity families such as young acting couple Yuan Hong and Zhang Xinyi and roommates like Wang Sulong and You Zhangjing discuss how to share household responsibilities.  Chen Yunyun, the show's producer, said that it is not easy for women in China today to manage their responsibilities at work and home. She said she hopes the show will inspire discussion about this issue. Show director Feng Jun noted that men have a responsibility to help with housework as well.  
